OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fmostly dying out but thickening cloud
OL,7,Fbringing patchy light rain to the west
OL,8,Fcoast later this evening. The patchy
OL,9,Flight rain extending eastwards
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FThe west staying mostly
OL,13,Fcloudy, but much of the light rain and
OL,14,Fdrizzle dying out. Brighter spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping around Inverness and the
OL,16,FMoray Firth and feeling quite warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
