OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain Wednesday, heavy at
OL,7,Ftimes and turning to snow over the
OL,8,Fmountains. Rain or showers on Thursday
OL,9,Fand Friday, which may be heavy. Winds
OL,10,Fstrengthening Friday, gales possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
